Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.50,0:22:43.82,ED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\an7}歌唱森林之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.53,0:22:46.75,ED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}希望你不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.87,0:22:49.26,ED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}我默默许下愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.72,0:22:52.11,ED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}你笑着说道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.31,0:22:54.63,ED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}我不会走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.08,0:22:57.38,ED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}你握住了我想要确认
